CodeSystem: specimen-source

specimen-source

The specimen analyzed. The current value set is taken from the SNOMED CT Body substance sample (specimen) hierarchy without the word 'specimen'. More values will be added as needed.

This code system http://www.fhir.org/guides/mfhir/CodeSystem/specimen-source defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
interstitial fluid interstitial fluid
capillary blood capillary blood
plasma plasma
serum serum
tears tears
whole blood whole blood
